snippet.title: Gummy World Trailer [HD]
snippet.description:
Follow Lewis the Adventurer as he travels to exciting new worlds collecting elusive Gummies and saving them from invasive Chameleons and other dangers. Connect Gummy Drops to create fun Combinations and Power Ups and collect all the different species!

Download Here!
https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/gummy-drops/id898519372?ls=1&mt=8

For more updates check out:
www.trilbygames.com
